{"id":26870,"title":"[Review of materials of the Fourth European Venous Forum (Stockholm, Sweden)].","abstract":"The article provides a brief review of the opinions and experience of the leading phlebologists from various countries, reflecting the latest updates and current problems regarding state-of-the-art management of diseases of major veins of lower extremities. Special attention is focussed on deep vein thromboses and consequence thereof, as well as varicose disease. This is followed by description of novel approaches to treatment of the pathology concerned.","date":"2014-07-30","categories":"Cardiovascular Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25076511","annotations":[{"name":"Disease","weight":0.736795,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Pathology","weight":0.714353,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pathology"},{"name":"Deep vein thrombosis","weight":0.469544,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deep_vein_thrombosis"},{"name":"Sweden","weight":0.395147,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sweden"},{"name":"Vein","weight":0.331959,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vein"},{"name":"Thrombosis","weight":0.181098,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thrombosis"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.175016,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Novel","weight":0.135948,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Novel"},{"name":"Country","weight":0.0805305,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Country"},{"name":"Varicose veins","weight":0.0706647,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Varicose_veins"},{"name":"Stockholm","weight":0.0477563,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stockholm"},{"name":"Management","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management"},{"name":"Ethnic groups in Europe","weight":0.0300804,"wikipedia_article":"http://